==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Passeriformes
<hw>Passeriformes</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The largest order of
birds comprising about half the known species: rooks; finches; sparrows;
tits; warblers; robins; wrens; swallows; etc.; in four suborders:
<subord>Eurylaimi</subord>; <subord>Tyranni</subord>;
<subord>Menurae</subord>; <subord>Oscines</subord> or
<subord>Passeres</subord>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order Passeriformes.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Passerina</ent>⟦br⟧
